#### Bad solution
I found a solution to add an empty actor on the first row, but it seems not good :)
```java
public InfoButton(String text, int numberText, TextButtonStyle style, LabelStyle numberLabelStyle) {
	super(text, style);
	numberLabel = new Label(Integer.toString(numberText), numberLabelStyle);
	numberLabel.setAlignment(Align.center);

	add().row(); // <-- a bad solution

	add(numberLabel).expand().top();
}
```

